butes": {"content": "但你沒有任何鬆了一口氣的感覺。"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玩鬧可以到此為止嗎？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$3"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_act1mainss_bat1_intro", "key": "$m_act1mainss_bat1_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drkcludsthdr", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "d"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "d", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "怎麼回事……！", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line250"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$3"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這怎麼會——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$3"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士、阿米婭，後退！", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#7$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有力的反抗，AMa-10，你的計劃奏效了。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誠如你所說，現在你們的確有殺死我的機會……", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，只是一個用源石塑造出的替身，就會讓你如此慌張嗎？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#10$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……！", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#6$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "AMa-10，我無意與你辯論你信奉的價值。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#10$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一直以來所堅持的事，它們太渺小，我甚至無法找到一種可信的邏輯架構來評價它們的意義。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#10$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是實驗中的確會出現這樣的情況，一些細小的誤差，最終造成了巨大的妨礙。我不得不接受這樣的結果。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#10$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很遺憾，要將你當作這個誤差來抹除。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#10$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crystalrise", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 0.4, "loop": "true", "channel": "e"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 90.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "e", "fadetime": 6.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "普瑞賽斯抬起了手。"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "源石再次開始生長，結晶構成的尖銳的枝椏在你與阿米婭的