難，但我認同它的意義。"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於未來，你會有自己的答案，我只能這樣堅持。"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用太擔心我的事情，羅德島不應當脆弱到離開了某人就無法前行。"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的願望？"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的願望就是守護好你和阿米婭的願望。"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我立下的誓言我永遠不會背棄。儘管我們對守護的定義各不相同，但我會站在這裡，直到最後。"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們無法忘懷過去，但你會有不一樣的未來。"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_ac8mi_sidebyside_dusk", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 10.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經尋找到了自己生命的意義。"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請帶領羅德島……"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續走下去吧。"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "{@nickname}。"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_sys_act1mainss_intro", "key": "$m_sys_act1mainss_loop", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Subtitle", "att